(348, 3, '_wp_suggested_privacy_policy_content', 'a:3:{s:11:\"plugin_name\";s:26:\"WooCommerce Shipping & Tax\";s:11:\"policy_text\";s:305:\"<p>By using this extension, you may be storing personal data or sharing data with external services. <a href=\"https://jetpack.com/support/for-your-privacy-policy/#woocommerce-services\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more about how this works, including what you may want to include in your privacy policy.</a></p>\n\";s:5:\"added\";i:1621794607;}'),
